Revision history for App-osnames

0.10    2015-09-15 (PERLANCAR)

	- [ux] Allow displaying result as text table under
	  Perinci::CmdLine::Lite, by converting tags to comma-separated
	  string.

	- [ux] Change -V to -l (mnemonic: ls -l).


0.09    2015-09-03 (PERLANCAR)

	- No functional changes.

	- [dist] Move spec prereqs from RuntimeRequires to
	  DevelopRecommends to reduce deps but still allow indicating spec
	  requirement.


0.08    2015-07-01 (PERLANCAR)

	- No functional changes.

	- Adjust to Perinci::Sub::Gen::AccessTable 0.46.


0.07    2014-12-18 (PERLANCAR)

	- Split data to Perl-osnames.


0.06    2014-12-18 (PERLANCAR)

	- Add tag: posix, document the tags.


0.05     2014-08-16 (SHARYANTO) - Happy 19th CPAN Day!

         - [build] CLI scripts are now generated automatically using
           Dist::Zilla::Plugin::ScriptFromFunc. The plugin is still at 0.01 so the
           generated script is not as polished as it should be. Stay tuned.


0.04     2014-07-22 (SHARYANTO)

         - No functional changes.

         - Switch CLI scripts from using Perinci::CmdLine to
           Perinci::CmdLine::Any to reduce size of dependencies.


0.03    2013-10-26 (SHARYANTO)

        - Allow specifying query in first argument.

        - Add examples.


0.02    2013-09-12 (SHARYANTO)

        - Add -V alias for --detail for convenience.

        - Force use of Perinci::Sub::Gen::AccessTable 0.23 which hints correct
          column order.


0.01    2013-09-11 (SHARYANTO)

        - First release.
